# EduGuide - The Stress-Free Homework Partner

A pedagogical web app that helps children (ages 10-15) understand their homework through scaffolding, without revealing answers. Students can photograph homework, get questions reformulated, and earn XP — all in a stress-free, accessible interface.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **API Keys Required**: This app uses **Google Vision API** (OCR) and **Google Gemini API** (reasoning). You'll need to provide API keys before Phase 3. Are you set up with Google Cloud credentials, or would you prefer mock/simulated API responses for initial development?

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Scope for v1**: This plan builds a full working prototype. The **Parent Dashboard** will show progress data but uses a simple PIN-based access (not full authentication). The **Teacher/School integration** mentioned in the draft is deferred to a future version. Does this scope sound right?

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Language**: The UI copy in the spec is English, but the first draft is in Swedish and mentions your daughter. Should the app UI be in **Swedish**, **English**, or **bilingual**?

---

## Proposed Changes

### Project Structure

```
EduGuide/
├── app.py                  # Flask app entry point
├── config.py               # Configuration (API keys, DB settings)
├── models.py               # SQLAlchemy database models
├── requirements.txt        # Python dependencies
├── static/
│   ├── css/
│   │   └── style.css       # Full design system
│   ├── js/
│   │   ├── app.js          # Main app logic
│   │   ├── camera.js       # Camera/image upload handling
│   │   ├── tts.js          # Text-to-Speech module
│   │   └── rewards.js      # XP animations & tracking
│   └── images/
│       └── (persona icons, badges, etc.)
├── templates/
│   ├── base.html           # Base layout with nav & accessibility controls
│   ├── index.html          # Landing / persona selection
│   ├── study.html          # Main homework helper (chat-style)
│   └── parent.html         # Parent dashboard
└── services/
    ├── __init__.py
    ├── ocr_service.py      # Google Vision OCR wrapper
    ├── ai_service.py       # Gemini scaffolding & reasoning
    └── xp_service.py       # XP calculation & rewards logic
```

