### Phase 2: Student Mode UI

#### [NEW] [style.css](file:///e:/EgnaStudier/1.%20Egna%20studier%20-%20välsorterad/Antigravity_IDE/EduGuide/static/css/style.css)
- Anti-stress color palette: soft purples, teals, warm whites — no harsh reds
- Large base font (18px), clear hierarchy
